ehicles, generating leads, and applying for loans and trade advances. Additionally, it operates Payswiff, an omnichannel payment transaction solution that lets business owners accept payments from their customers in-store, at-home deliveries, online and on-the-go using mPOS, and POS solutions. The company was incorporated in 1978 and is headquartered in Chennai, India."}}